Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.50,0:00:41.06,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Cold winter fast approaches as we fearfully wait
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.25,0:00:45.34,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The simplest of simple creatures bound by the laws of fate
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.60,0:00:47.81,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,As we shivered in the gutters
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.60,0:00:50.21,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Far away from home~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.70,0:00:53.17,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We lost the last vestige of hope~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:54.86,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Freezing and alone
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.58,0:00:59.85,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,A shadow came to us in our dreams with tales of better times~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.34,0:01:04.42,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The royal Princess of the Night forgave us for our crimes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.58,0:01:09.41,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And as the Solar Sister overlooked us, nocturnal we became~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.94,0:01:14.03,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We wore a darker armor, and we carried a different flame
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.04,0:01:16.88,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You now belong to a greater good
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.21,0:01:18.90,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And you answer to a higher call!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.99,0:01:21.67,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You are part of the best and greatest
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.79,0:01:23.44,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And there is no room for failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.90,0:01:26.55,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You will leave behind all weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.89,0:01:28.31,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You are no longer a mortal!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.78,0:01:31.61,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You are now indestructible
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.80,0:01:33.19,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Soldier of the Night!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.28,0:01:38.21,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,As the sunset fades away, the yellow turns to grey~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.70,0:01:42.83,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The moonlight shines across the land, a calling we obey
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.54,0:01:47.70,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The purest black of shadows rise to fight a greater fight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.41,0:01:52.46,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,My brothers and sisters move as one, we Soldiers of the Night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.54,0:01:59.78,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We stand at arms before our liege, each one of us just a pawn~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.08,0:02:04.61,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Now we reign supreme throughout the dark, until the light of dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.17,0:02:09.15,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The memories we have left behind us might cripple lesser men
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.34,0:02:14.14,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But those of us brought back from nothing have risen once again
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.85,0:02:18.86,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We see it in her moonlit eyes, a fury held at bay
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.05,0:02:23.51,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,A battle waiting in the ashes, to resume~ another day
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.93,0:02:28.39,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And as we disappear into the shadows, we fill their souls with dread
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.65,0:02:33.34,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We fight tonight to rule tomorrow, and a dark day lies ahead
